# Puck Blocks 环境变量配置模板

# ============================================
# 广告归因系统 - 必需配置
# ============================================

# Meta (Facebook) Conversions API
# 获取方式: https://business.facebook.com/events_manager
META_PIXEL_ID=123456789012345
META_CAPI_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_meta_access_token_here

# TikTok Events API
# 获取方式: https://business-api.tiktok.com/portal/docs
TIKTOK_PIXEL_CODE=ABCDEFGHIJK1234567
TIKTOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_tiktok_access_token_here

# Google Analytics 4 / Google Ads
# 获取方式: https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/
GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX
GA4_API_SECRET=your_ga4_api_secret_here

# ============================================
# 可选平台 (按需启用)
# ============================================

# Pinterest Conversions API
# 获取方式: https://developers.pinterest.com/
# PINTEREST_AD_ACCOUNT_ID=549764220326
# PINTEREST_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_pinterest_access_token_here

# Klaviyo CRM Events
# 获取方式: https://www.klaviyo.com/settings/account/api-keys
# KLAVIYO_PRIVATE_API_KEY=pk_your_private_key_here

# ============================================
# Cloudflare Workers 配置 (生产环境)
# ============================================

# 如果部署到 Cloudflare Workers，使用以下命令配置 Secrets:
# wrangler secret put META_PIXEL_ID
# wrangler secret put META_CAPI_ACCESS_TOKEN
# wrangler secret put TIKTOK_PIXEL_CODE
# wrangler secret put TIKTOK_ACCESS_TOKEN
# wrangler secret put GA4_MEASUREMENT_ID
# wrangler secret put GA4_API_SECRET

# ============================================
# 配置说明
# ============================================

# Meta Pixel ID:
#   - 位置: Events Manager > Data Sources > Pixel
#   - 格式: 15 位数字
#   - 示例: 123456789012345

# Meta CAPI Access Token:
#   - 位置: Events Manager > Settings > Conversions API
#   - 格式: 长字符串 (通常以 "EAA" 开头)
#   - 权限: ads_management, business_management

# TikTok Pixel Code:
#   - 位置: TikTok Ads Manager > Assets > Events
#   - 格式: 大写字母+数字 (17 位)
#   - 示例: ABCDEFGHIJK1234567

# TikTok Access Token:
#   - 位置: TikTok Business API > Authentication
#   - 格式: 长字符串
#   - 作用域: events, analytics

# GA4 Measurement ID:
#   - 位置: Google Analytics > Admin > Data Streams
#   - 格式: G-XXXXXXXXXX
#   - 示例: G-ABC123DEF4

# GA4 API Secret:
#   - 位置: Data Streams > Measurement Protocol API secrets
#   - 格式: 字母数字混合
#   - 用途: Server-side event tracking

# ============================================
# 测试配置
# ============================================

# 测试 Meta CAPI 连接:
# curl -X POST "https://graph.facebook.com/v21.0/{PIXEL_ID}/events?access_token={TOKEN}" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"data": [{"event_name": "PageView", "event_time": 1234567890, "action_source": "website"}]}'

# 测试 TikTok Events API:
# curl -X POST "https://business-api.tiktok.com/open_api/v1.3/event/track/" \
#   -H "Access-Token: {TOKEN}" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"pixel_code": "{PIXEL_CODE}", "event": "ViewContent", "timestamp": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z"}'

# 测试 GA4 Measurement Protocol:
# curl -X POST "https://www.google-analytics.com/mp/collect?measurement_id={ID}&api_secret={SECRET}" \
#   -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
#   -d '{"client_id": "test", "events": [{"name": "page_view"}]}'

# ============================================
# 安全建议
# ============================================

# ⚠️ 注意事项:
# 1. 永远不要将此文件提交到 Git (已在 .gitignore 中)
# 2. 使用环境变量管理工具 (如 Doppler, Vault)
# 3. 定期轮换 API Token (建议每 90 天)
# 4. 为不同环境使用不同的 Pixel/Token (dev/staging/prod)
# 5. 监控 API 请求配额，避免超限

# ============================================
# 部署检查清单
# ============================================

# 开发环境:
# ☐ 复制 .env.example 到 .env
# ☐ 填写所有必需的 API Token
# ☐ 运行 `bun dev` 测试本地开发

# 生产环境:
# ☐ 在 Cloudflare Workers 中配置 Secrets
# ☐ 验证 /api/jump 端点可访问
# ☐ 测试一次完整的转化流程
# ☐ 检查 Meta/TikTok/GA4 控制台是否收到事件

# ============================================
# 故障排查
# ============================================

# 问题: 广告平台未收到事件
# 解决:
# 1. 检查 Pixel ID 是否正确
# 2. 验证 Access Token 权限
# 3. 查看服务端日志 (console.error)
# 4. 确认 API 端点返回 200 OK

# 问题: 跳转延迟过长
# 解决:
# 1. 检查网络延迟 (ping api.tiktok.com)
# 2. 启用并行请求 (Promise.allSettled)
# 3. 设置 2s 超时
# 4. 添加 preconnect 标签

# 问题: Email 点击未跟踪
# 解决:
# 1. 确认 href 使用了 buildTrackingUrl()
# 2. 检查 /api/jump 端点是否支持 GET
# 3. 测试邮件中的链接是否正确

